<p>Welcome to Quizanchos!</p>

<section class="about-us">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>Quizanchos is a vibrant platform dedicated to making learning and knowledge sharing fun and engaging. We believe that everyone loves a good challenge, and our quizzes provide just that.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to create an environment where people of all ages can test their knowledge, learn something new, and compete with others in a friendly and entertaining way.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Our team consists of passionate educators, developers, and designers who work tirelessly to ensure that you have the best quiz-taking experience possible. We’re here to inspire learning and curiosity.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or suggestions, feel free to reach out to us via the <a href="/Contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
</section>